title: Why am I running against Jaime Herrera Beutler.mp4
description:
Published on May 31, 2014 by Elect Michael Delavar

What could be so important that it would make me challenge Herrera Beutler in a primary race? Her deplorable record on liberty. JHB has voted to give the president the power to detain indefinitely anyone based upon an accusation of being associated with a terrorist. Freedom died a little when JHB voted for that. And she has done it more than once.

Jaime Herrera Beutler is the Congressional Representative from the 3rd District of Southwest Washington State. She voted to continue the NDAA and to define when it could apply to US Citizens on US soil. For more Search Youtube for "Congress responds to NDAA
